ygData.messageBody:
You have to go along the shore to the right of the docks where the boat comes in. There is a lone man fishing there. Swim into the water directly in front of him. There is a lone shark there and the box is underneath it.
----- Original Message -----
From: Michael Cherin
To: eq_wizards@onelist.com
Cc: EQ_Innoruuk@onelist.com
Sent: Tuesday, July 06, 1999 9:54 AM
Subject: [eq_wizards] Journal Strongbox Quest (Freeport)


Has anybody done the journal strongbox quest in freeport? I keep getting told that the journal strongbox I need to get is in the water by the freeport docks but I cannot find it! I've tried killing the sharks to see if it was loot, and I didn't get any loot. Can anybody who is familiar with this quest help?

Thanks,

Michael Cherin
